<p>The installation screen gives you a short introduction into phpBB. It allows you to read the license phpBB 3.0 is released under (the <a href="http://opensource.org/licenses/gpl-license.php" target="_top">General Public License</a>) and provides information about how you can receive support. To start the installation, click the <span class="guilabel">Install</span> tab (see <a href="quick_installation.php#img_quick_installation_intro" title="Figure 1.1. Introduction">Figure 1.1, “Introduction”</a>).</p>